Subject: [PATCH 4.19 106/113] hpet: Fix division by zero in hpet_time_div()
Date:   Mon, 29 Jul 2019 21:23:13 +0200
Message-Id: <20190729190720.652873366@linuxfoundation.org>
X-Mailer: git-send-email 2.22.0
